data.description: Stunning surroundings showcase a three-bedroom, three-full-bath home complemented by a very spacious finished basement. The main level boasts an open floor plan, while the lower level features a generous family room and two additional bonus rooms. This home offers a lot of finished square footage. Situated on a sprawling 5-acre property, this home also includes a barn and a partially fenced patio area. Conveniently located, this property provides effortless access to major highways, ensuring a seamless lifestyle. Home is being sold As-Is, seller will make no repairs or provide inspections.
